serial2uinput by Alexander Grothe 2011 - 2012

serial2uinput requires python-uinput V 0.6.1. or higher. Additional required packages are libudev0 and libudev-dev.

### Fetch the code for python-uinput from it's git: ###
#
# git clone git://github.com/tuomasjjrasanen/python-uinput.git
# cd python-uinput
# git clone git://github.com/tuomasjjrasanen/libsuinput.git
# sudo python setup.py install
#
###

serial2uinput must be run as superuser or with sufficent rights to create an uinput device
